{"tid":419374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大「骯髒中餐廳」電話遊戲　被質疑侮辱華人","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T06:32:18.000Z","uid":53379,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"06b7cb3ce483906c75e40b8199d29793d837bece","tid":419374,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加拿大「骯髒中餐廳」電話遊戲　被質疑侮辱華人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170930/s00005/31a966c3ce3db2ecd30a6ee984c79466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170930%2Fs00005%2F31a966c3ce3db2ecd30a6ee984c79466.jpg&h=6c4f4810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加拿大一個名為《Dirty Chinese Restaurant》（骯髒中餐廳）的手機遊戲，被質疑帶有種族歧視成分，侮辱華人。有美國華裔議員炮轟該遊戲，用盡所有對美籍華人的負面定型，要求各平台不要讓遊戲上架。中國領事館發言人則稱，遊戲充斥辱華內容，要求開發商停止開發，並公開道歉。<br />\n<br />\n這個由加拿大公司Big-O-Tree Games開發的《Dirty Chinese Restaurant》手機遊戲中，玩家化身為華裔老闆Wong Fu，作出不同選項經營餐廳，包括僱用員工和購入食材等。但當中有些選項為追斬貓狗，煮給顧客食；亦有血汗工廠方式經營的選項。另從預告片段中，可見老闆從垃圾桶撿出食材、在餐廳聚賭、顧客嘔吐、甚至老闆殺人等畫面。<br />\n<br />\n美國首位美籍華裔聯邦眾議員孟昭文（Grace Meng），在社交網站發文炮轟該遊戲，指遊戲用盡了所有對美籍華人的負面定型，明顯對華人帶有偏見。她對於遊戲即將上架感到震驚，認為遊戲是針對美籍華人的種族主義之縮影，促請Google和Apple等平台不要讓遊戲上架。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這種爭議或許早在遊戲開發商Big-O-Tree Games公司預期之內，網站首頁寫著「因為政治正確太過沉悶&hellip;&hellip;」公司發言人蘭布羅普洛斯接受當地傳媒訪問時表示，遊戲並非準確地表達中國文化，指遊戲主要是受《South Park》（衰仔樂園）等經典的政治不正確節目影響，帶有諷刺及喜劇成分。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐多倫多總領事館周六（9月30日）就事件發表聲明，譴責遊戲充斥種族主義及辱華內容，指很多華人透過工作為加拿大發展作出貢獻，認為凡是公平正義的社會和有道德良知的人，都不會容忍這種行為。領事館要求開發商立即停止開發、出售並從網上移除該遊戲，以及公開正式道歉。<br />\n<br />\n霍士新聞報道稱，Big-O-Tree Games代表未能肯定遊戲將於何時推出。<br />\n<br />\n（霍士新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170930/s00005/1506758055193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170930%2Fs00005%2F1506758055193&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3aa56a6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170930%2Fs00005%2F1506758055193&h=9c4c0fee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170930/s00005/1506758055193</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明講緊中國人係要拖華人落水"},{"pid":"9ed60d7148997dbb535ac455ade3b800008b6268","tid":419374,"uid":134474,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:23:24.000Z","msg":"呢個真係事實嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872108a1e05777d2a1bc1c8cdf6ea6b5a6e0e11a","tid":419374,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個真係事實嚟<br />\n話人歧視做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你同我心底都知中餐廳就係咁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"aa61272d9b948083901a9a908ce5a89c3a0a0d99","tid":419374,"uid":55458,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:25:51.000Z","msg":"ooohhh ching chong ling long ting tong"},{"pid":"7afa35a6eb365250c11b17a54a988635fec22dee","tid":419374,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢個真係事實嚟<br />\n話人歧視做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你同我心底都知中餐廳就係咁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea67e005f5dd72d657a89ff115b947e81afd71c","tid":419374,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"求apps名"},{"pid":"d0c9f17fe307d6b8eeec71b9dde596cabb8de6e2","tid":419374,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:34:27.000Z","msg":"華人？<br />\n係你地支那人渣"},{"pi